{"id":613161,"date":[{"year":1981,"month":5,"day":10}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"五月诗抄","genre":"","count":"165","ytitle":"","mtitle":"春在庐山","ftitle":"","authors":["吴奔星"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴奔星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在哪里?春天!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一路呼喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路追赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从塞北撵到江南——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“跃上葱笼四百旋”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊!春天，你也上庐山!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个山谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一座山峦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"覆盖长青的草木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显示碧绿的容颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然季节是初夏之间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却到处是春意盎然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁花铺地，林木参天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少飞瀑，多少流泉——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是春天的脉搏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是生命的能源。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何暴风雨的摧残，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都只能装点庐山的春天。"}]}